# CODEOWNERS — CyberSkill landing-page
#
# Each line: <path-pattern> <@owner ...>
# GitHub auto-requests review from the listed owner(s) on any PR that touches the path.
#
# References: AGENTS.md §16 (Self-amendment) · FR-PERF-001 §7 row 8 (budget governance) ·
#             FR-DS-002 §1 #7 (palette immutability) · FR-CMS-001 §1 #4 (no 8th scene)
#
# The patterns below are ordered most-specific-first (CODEOWNERS uses last-match-wins
# within a single file — the most specific path SHOULD appear later).

# --- baseline: everything has founder review by default ---
